data.description: Located on a Culdesac with a large backyard and a fire pit for those cool evenings! This 4-bedroom Home has New Carpet Upstairs and New Vinyl Plank Flooring just installed on the main.  The large Kitchen has Stainless Appliances and an Island and is open to the Living Room. There is also a large formal dining room off the 2-story foyer. All Bedrooms are upstairs and the Master has a tray ceiling, whirlpool tub, separate shower, double vanity, and a walk-in closet! The garage has a finished floor and an extra refrigerator. Seller will pay off Solar panels at closing with an acceptable offer! The Amenity Center has a pool, playground, and tennis. Welcome to Stonebridge Subdivision! Kroger Grocery and several Restaurants are nearby off Berwick Blvd and Hwy 17.
